spec_data.Name: perl-HTML-GenToc
spec_data.Description:
HTML::GenToc generates anchors and a table of contents for HTML documents.
Depending on the arguments, it will insert the information it generates, or
output to a string, a separate file or STDOUT.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 12:09:04 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Generate a Table of Contents for HTML documents
